Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:02.97,SIGN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs72\pos(362,364)}Charge
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.86,0:00:17.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next, about Misora Naomi, {\alpha&HFF&}isn't it about time that we open up the investigation to the public?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.63,0:00:20.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next, about Misora Naomi, isn't it about time that we open up the investigation to the public?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.32,0:00:23.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we do, we should try to avoid any connections being made to the Kira case.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.04,0:00:25.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Use an artist's impression rather than a photo.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.90,0:00:26.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, {\alpha&HFF&}it's already been four months since she vanished.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.80,0:00:29.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, it's already been four months since she vanished.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.11,0:00:31.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can only imagine that she's dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.63,0:00:35.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if she's dead, it's strange that no one has been able to locate her body yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.88,0:00:39.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we can find it, it may shed some light on this situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.93,0:00:41.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuzaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.14,0:00:42.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sakura TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.88,0:00:44.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something terrible is occurring.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.23,0:00:49.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Basically, we're presenting this broadcast as Kira's hostages, {\alpha&HFF&}but also as reporters fulfilling their duties.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.07,0:00:52.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Basically, we're presenting this broadcast as Kira's hostages, but also as reporters fulfilling their duties.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.83,0:00:58.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please understand that we would never air this broadcast with an intent to deceive or with a wish to gain popularity.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.10,0:01:00.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kira's hostages?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.75,0:01:02.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.15,0:01:04.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Four days ago, {\alpha&HFF&}the director on duty received these four tapes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.16,0:01:07.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Four days ago, the director on duty received these four tapes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.69,0:01:11.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Without a doubt, they have been sent by Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.16,0:01:13.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our ratings will rise by 60%... {\alpha&HFF&}no, 70% at least!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.13,0:01:16.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our ratings will rise by 60%... no, 70% at least!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.74,0:01:23.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The first tape contained predictions of the date and times of death for two suspects that were recently apprehended.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.33,0:01:29.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yesterday both suspects died at exactly their predicted times of death.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.67,0:01:31.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If that is really true, {\alpha&HFF&}it's definitely something only Kira can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.52,0:01:34.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If that is really true, it's definitely something only Kira can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.41,0:01:42.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've received orders from Kira to play this second tape today at exactly 5:59pm.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.53,0:01:46.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've been informed that this will contain a predicted murder as further proof that they are Kira, {\alpha&HFF&}and also a message to the people of the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.67,0:01:50.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've been informed that this will contain a predicted murder as further proof that they are Kira, and also a message to the people of the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.58,0:01:51.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-{\alpha&HFF&}Are you sure that this isn't another joke?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.87,0:01:53.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-Are you sure that this isn't another joke?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.90,0:01:54.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Surely... {\alpha&HFF&}no one would pull a prank that's this sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.94,0:01:58.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Surely... no one would pull a prank that's this sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.12,0:01:59.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.32,0:02:08.85,KiraVideo,,0000,0000,0000,,I am Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.22,0:02:17.82,KiraVideo,,0000,0000,0000,,If this video is being broadcast at exactly 5:59pm on the 18th of April, it should now be 5:59pm and 47... {\alpha&HFF&}48... 49...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.82,0:02:19.06,KiraVideo,,0000,0000,0000,,If this video is being broadcast at exactly 5:59pm on the 18th of April, it should now be 5:59pm and 47... 48... {\alpha&HFF&}49...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.06,0:02:20.44,KiraVideo,,0000,0000,0000,,If this video is being broadcast at exactly 5:59pm on the 18th of April, it should now be 5:59pm and 47... 48... 49...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.44,0:02:22.91,KiraVideo,,0000,0000,0000,,Please change the channel to Taiyou TV now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.91,0:02:25.76,KiraVideo,,0000,0000,0000,,The main newsreader, Hibima Kazuhiko, {\alpha&HFF&}will die of a heart attack at exactly 6 o'clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.76,0:02:28.02,KiraVideo,,0000,0000,0000,,The main newsreader, Hibima Kazuhiko, will die of a heart attack at exactly 6 o'clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.74,0:02:29.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Change it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.81,0:02:33.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.47,0:02:33.02,Background,,0000,0000,0000,,You okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.02,0:02:33.98,Background,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop filming!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.98,0:02:34.90,Background,,0000,0000,0000,,I said turn it off!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.90,0:02:35.75,Background,,0000,0000,0000,,Get help!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.75,0:02:37.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare they...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.85,0:02:39.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Change the channel back.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.28,0:02:43.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, bring me another TV. {\alpha&HFF&}No, make that two.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.00,0:02:44.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, bring me another TV. No, make that two.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.82,0:02:44.10,KiraVideo,,0000,0000,0000,,Hibima Kazuhiko continued to air his claims that Kira is evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.10,0:02:45.39,KiraVideo,,0000,0000,0000,,This is his due.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.10,0:02:45.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.89,0:02:48.72,KiraVideo,,0000,0000,0000,,Another sacrifice will have to be made.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.72,0:02:52.65,KiraVideo,,0000,0000,0000,,The target will be someone currently live on NHN TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.65,0:02:55.20,KiraVideo,,0000,0000,0000,,A commentator who's been negative about me, {\alpha&HFF&}Kobaizumi Seiji.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.20,0:02:56.73,KiraVideo,,0000,0000,0000,,A commentator who's been negative about me, Kobaizumi Seiji.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.20,0:02:58.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuzaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.21,0:02:59.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Turn to channel 24.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.20,0:03:03.45,Background,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?! Pull yourself together!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.79,0:03:03.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please change it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.51,0:03:08.75,KiraVideo,,0000,0000,0000,,I think that, by now, you should all believe that I am Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.78,0:03:14.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kira said that they wanted to send a message to the world, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.46,0:03:16.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've got to stop this broadcast, or there will be trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.38,0:03:20.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll phone Sakura TV!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.49,0:03:22.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No good, {\alpha&HFF&}my acquaintance at the station has his phone switched off.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.56,0:03:25.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No good, my acquaintance at the station has his phone switched off.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.51,0:03:27.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what part of the station I ring it's all busy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.64,0:03:29.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Screw this...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.19,0:03:31.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ukita-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.12,0:03:33.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go to the station in person and make them stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.28,0:03:37.82,KiraVideo,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, listen carefully, {\alpha&HFF&}I don't want to kill innocent people.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.82,0:03:40.78,KiraVideo,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, listen carefully, I don't want to kill innocent people.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.78,0:03:42.36,KiraVideo,,0000,0000,0000,,I hate evil, {\alpha&HFF&}and love justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.36,0:03:43.95,KiraVideo,,0000,0000,0000,,I hate evil, and love justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.21,0:03:48.66,KiraVideo,,0000,0000,0000,,I even regard the police as my ally, and not as my enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.25,0:03:50.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you, Kira...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.92,0:03:54.92,KiraVideo,,0000,0000,0000,,My wish is to create a world without any evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.35,0:03:57.31,KiraVideo,,0000,0000,0000,,If you all decide similarly, {\alpha&HFF&}it should be easy to achieve.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.31,0:03:59.34,KiraVideo,,0000,0000,0000,,If you all decide similarly, it should be easy to achieve.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.42,0:04:01.71,KiraVideo,,0000,0000,0000,,If you cease your attempts to capture me, {\alpha&HFF&}no innocent people will die.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.71,0:04:03.85,KiraVideo,,0000,0000,0000,,If you cease your attempts to capture me, no innocent people will die.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.85,0:04:05.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.50,0:04:07.96,KiraVideo,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you don't agree with me, {\alpha&HFF&}as long as you don't go to the media, or express it publicly, I won't kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.96,0:04:11.19,KiraVideo,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you don't agree with me, as long as you don't go to the media, or express it publicly, {\alpha&HFF&}I won't kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.19,0:04:13.28,KiraVideo,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you don't agree with me, as long as you don't go to the media, or express it publicly, I won't kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.28,0:04:16.63,KiraVideo,,0000,0000,0000,,Please try and wait a while; {\alpha&HFF&}this world will become something that anyone would appreciate.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.63,0:04:19.70,KiraVideo,,0000,0000,0000,,Please try and wait a while; this world will become something that anyone would appreciate.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.70,0:04:27.53,KiraVideo,,0000,0000,0000,,I will change this filthy world into a world that's build for gentle people.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.88,0:04:29.82,KiraVideo,,0000,0000,0000,,Try to imagine this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.82,0:04:31.79,KiraVideo,,0000,0000,0000,,The police and I will creat--
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.17,0:04:36.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sachiko...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.53,0:04:40.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Darling, {\alpha&HFF&}this is bad for your health. Please try to get some rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.95,0:04:42.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Darling, this is bad for your health. {\alpha&HFF&}Please try to get some rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.94,0:04:44.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Darling, this is bad for your health. Please try to get some rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.57,0:04:49.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sachiko... {\alpha&HFF&}I'm the Chief of the Kira Special Investigation Unit.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.31,0:04:52.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sachiko... I'm the Chief of the Kira Special Investigation Unit.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.97,0:05:05.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shit! It's shut!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.06,0:05:08.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Police! {\alpha&HFF&}Open up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.45,0:05:10.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Police! Open up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.70,0:05:12.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiots!!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.60,0:05:39.61,Background,,0000,0000,0000,,We interrupt this program to bring you live footage from outside the Sakura TV station!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.01,0:05:35.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello? {\alpha&HFF&}Damn it! I can't get through.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.49,0:05:37.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello? Damn it! I can't get through.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.55,0:05:39.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aizawa-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.21,0:05:48.74,Background,,0000,0000,0000,,As you can see, someone has collapsed!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.11,0:05:52.24,Background,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the scene occuring outside Sakura TV right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.87,0:05:55.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ukita-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.06,0:05:57.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Shit!! Was it Kira?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.79,0:06:00.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aizawa-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.02,0:06:02.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where do you think you're going?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.92,0:06:05.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To Ukita, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.36,0:06:06.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.80,0:06:08.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please compose yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.42,0:06:11.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you telling me to just shut up and watch TV?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.46,0:06:13.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If this is Kira's work, {\alpha&HFF&}and you go there, the same thing will happen to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.54,0:06:15.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If this is Kira's work, and you go there, the same thing will happen to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.88,0:06:19.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If Kira doesn't have a name, they shouldn't be able to kill!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.35,0:06:21.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So why has this happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.52,0:06:24.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Were the fake IDs useless?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.15,0:06:28.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe... Kira already knew our names?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.20,0:06:30.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a possibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.12,0:06:32.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if Kira did know that, {\alpha&HFF&}it would have been a lot easier for them to kill us first.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.68,0:06:37.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if Kira did know that, it would have been a lot easier for them to kill us first.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.25,0:06:38.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,According to my theory, {\alpha&HFF&}Kira needs a name and a face, but having watched this,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.61,0:06:41.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,According to my theory, Kira needs a name and a face, {\alpha&HFF&}but having watched this,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.21,0:06:42.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,According to my theory, Kira needs a name and a face, but having watched this,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.80,0:06:45.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it seems that the probability of Kira being able to kill someone solely by knowing their face, {\alpha&HFF&}isn't zero.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.20,0:06:46.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it seems that the probability of Kira being able to kill someone solely by knowing their face, isn't zero.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.46,0:06:51.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, the only think that I can say, {\alpha&HFF&}is that Kira is inside the station, or at least somewhere where they can monitor the people entering--
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.10,0:06:53.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, the only think that I can say, is that Kira is inside the station, {\alpha&HFF&}or at least somewhere where they can monitor the people entering--
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.30,0:06:58.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, the only think that I can say, is that Kira is inside the station, or at least somewhere where they can monitor the people entering--
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.72,0:06:59.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you think that Kira is around that area, {\alpha&HFF&}there's even more of a reason to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.14,0:07:01.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you think that Kira is around that area, there's even more of a reason to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.37,0:07:05.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's always the possibility that they set up surveillance cameras.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.16,0:07:08.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you carelessly rush out there now, you'll only be killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.16,0:07:11.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You! I thought that you were risking your life to catch Kira!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.89,0:07:14.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Risking your life, {\alpha&HFF&}and allowing someone to easily take it, are two completely different things.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.12,0:07:19.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Risking your life, and allowing someone to easily take it are two completely different things.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.00,0:07:20.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.79,0:07:27.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Try and hold back.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.08,0:07:29.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that Ukita-san has been killed, {\alpha&HFF&}if you were to lose your life too...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.36,0:07:33.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that Ukita-san has been killed, if you were to lose your life too...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.14,0:07:43.33,KiraVideo,,0000,0000,0000,,To the police; please decide whether you will cooperate with me in creating a new world, and announce your answer of "yes" or "no" in four days' time,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.33,0:07:47.20,KiraVideo,,0000,0000,0000,,during the 6 o'clock news on the 22nd of April.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.20,0:07:52.32,KiraVideo,,0000,0000,0000,,I have prepared videos for both "yes" and "no" responses.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.05,0:08:17.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.48,0:08:18.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! {\alpha&HFF&}What do you think you're playing at?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.40,0:08:19.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! What do you think you're playing at?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.28,0:08:25.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's the studio that's airing the Kira tapes?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.63,0:08:29.57,Background,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a patrol van! A patrol van has charged into Sakura TV!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.49,0:08:33.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's one way of entering the station without revealing your identity...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.86,0:08:36.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.71,0:08:37.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Police! {\alpha&HFF&}Stop the broadcast!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.86,0:08:39.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Police! Stop the broadcast!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.71,0:08:39.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-{\alpha&HFF&}What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.95,0:08:40.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.90,0:08:43.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm telling you to stop the Kira tapes!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.27,0:08:43.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-{\alpha&HFF&}Wait a second Detective. If we stop this tape, we'll be killed by Kira...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.99,0:08:46.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait a second Detective. {\alpha&HFF&}If we stop this tape, we'll be killed by Kira...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.19,0:08:49.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait a second Detective. If we stop this tape, we'll be killed by Kira...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.21,0:08:51.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hand them over!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.51,0:08:54.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you do that, you can save your life right now, if nothing else.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.38,0:08:55.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-{\alpha&HFF&}What are you thinking?! Are you insane?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.21,0:08:58.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What are you thinking?! Are you insane?
Comment: 0,0:08:58.97,0:09:08.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,EYECATCHERS
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.35,0:09:12.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the result of you covering the Kira case as though they are some kind of star.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.97,0:09:14.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"You reap what you sow", don't you agree?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.28,0:09:17.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want all the copies as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.62,0:09:19.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't even think about trying to get out of this now!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.62,0:09:20.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O-{\alpha&HFF&}Okay! I'll get them, I'll get them, so stop waving that pistol around!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.08,0:09:21.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay! {\alpha&HFF&}I'll get them, I'll get them, so stop waving that pistol around!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.30,0:09:24.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay! I'll get them, I'll get them, so stop waving that pistol around!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.85,0:09:27.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your eyes are crazy...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.15,0:09:32.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Finally, a single police car has arrived outside Sakura TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.75,0:09:34.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So we're not the only ones... {\alpha&HFF&}there are still others in the force that want to stand up and fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.51,0:09:38.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So we're not the only ones... there are still others in the force that want to stand up and fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.15,0:09:40.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aizawa-san, {\alpha&HFF&}you know the cell phone number of Deputy Chief Kitamura, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.21,0:09:43.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aizawa-san, you know the cell phone number of Deputy Chief Kitamura, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.09,0:09:50.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aizawa, I thought that I told you not to call me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.30,0:09:51.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is L. {\alpha&HFF&}I'd like to ask a favor of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.89,0:09:54.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is L. I'd like to ask a favor of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.58,0:09:55.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Upon seeing this broadcast, {\alpha&HFF&}people connected with the police will act, driven by their own sense of personal justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.94,0:09:59.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Upon seeing this broadcast, people connected with the police will act, driven by their own sense of personal justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.90,0:10:03.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like you to control this directly from the top, or this could turn into a disaster.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.51,0:10:07.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But on this case, we're...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.31,0:10:13.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Both of the policemen that rushed to the scene have collapsed!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.40,0:10:13.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-{\alpha&HFF&}We will also be evacuating the area!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.90,0:10:17.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-We will also be evacuating the area!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.20,0:10:20.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood. L, {\alpha&HFF&}please advise me on how I should command.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.00,0:10:23.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood. L, please advise me on how I should command.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.85,0:10:28.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Chief Yagami.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.94,0:10:31.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Call him back, and hand me the phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.39,0:10:33.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please hurry and let me talk to Ryuuzaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.65,0:10:35.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's me. {\alpha&HFF&}Yagami-san, so it was you in the patrol van.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.03,0:10:36.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's me. Yagami-san, {\alpha&HFF&}so it was you in the patrol van.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.25,0:10:38.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's me. Yagami-san, so it was you in the patrol van.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.33,0:10:39.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes... {\alpha&HFF&}I couldn't stop myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.54,0:10:41.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes... I couldn't stop myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.74,0:10:43.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've seized all the tapes, {\alpha&HFF&}and I'll bring them over to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.74,0:10:45.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've seized all the tapes, and I'll bring them over to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.42,0:10:47.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.76,0:10:49.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel more than alright. {\alpha&HFF&}In fact, I've never felt this alive before!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.46,0:10:52.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel more than alright. In fact, I've never felt this alive before!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.79,0:10:55.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind that, what should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.16,0:10:57.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think the front entrace is dangerous, {\alpha&HFF&}but I should be fine in the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.44,0:10:59.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think the front entrace is dangerous, but I should be fine in the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.99,0:11:01.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.04,0:11:03.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Deputy Kitamura, {\alpha&HFF&}Chief Yagami was the one who charged into the station.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.34,0:11:05.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Deputy Kitamura, Chief Yagami was the one who charged into the station.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.00,0:11:07.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How are your preparations proceeding?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.59,0:11:09.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've done as you asked.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.08,0:11:11.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yagami-san, {\alpha&HFF&}please leave openly through the front entrance in five minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.30,0:11:14.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yagami-san, please leave openly through the front entrance in five minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.94,0:11:16.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Openly? Through the front entrance?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.20,0:11:46.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are to be no gaps! Understood?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.49,0:11:48.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ensure that you aren't seen!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.74,0:11:52.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kira won't be inside the station; if they're here, they're outside!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.13,0:12:05.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.12,0:12:08.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll drive myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.26,0:12:09.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.88,0:12:17.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen up!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.80,0:12:21.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a good chance that Kira may be somewhere within visual range.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.10,0:12:24.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Devise methods of searching that ensures you can't be seen.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.87,0:12:32.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The police have ignored Kira, and have shown us that they are ready to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.96,0:12:33.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-{\alpha&HFF&}It takes courage for me to say this... but what they are doing is right! This is right!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.94,0:12:37.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It takes courage for me to say this... {\alpha&HFF&}but what they are doing is right! This is right!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.41,0:12:39.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It takes courage for me to say this... but what they are doing is right! {\alpha&HFF&}This is right!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.14,0:12:40.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It takes courage for me to say this... but what they are doing is right! This is right!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.97,0:12:44.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the position a constitutional nation should take!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.07,0:12:47.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Tanakabara Kouki.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.13,0:12:51.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The announcer for NHN's "Golden news"... Tanakabara Kouki!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.41,0:12:55.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chief!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.68,0:12:57.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chief Yagami!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.81,0:13:00.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuzaki... {\alpha&HFF&}I apologize for acting on impulse.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.37,0:13:03.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuzaki... I apologize for acting on impulse.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.38,0:13:05.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems I got a little too emotional.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.09,0:13:06.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.90,0:13:11.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All the envelopes and tapes sent by Kira are in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.89,0:13:13.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.08,0:13:14.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L-{\alpha&HFF&}Let me rest for a while...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.77,0:13:17.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L-Let me rest for a while...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.57,0:13:21.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yagami-san, {\alpha&HFF&}I won't let this go to waste.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.42,0:13:23.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yagami-san, I won't let this go to waste.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.25,0:13:26.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's postmarked from Osaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.89,0:13:30.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, Kira is able to manipulate people before death, {\alpha&HFF&}so they wouldn't have to go to Osaka themselves to mail this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.44,0:13:33.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, Kira is able to manipulate people before death, so they wouldn't have to go to Osaka themselves to mail this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.46,0:13:35.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aizawa-san, {\alpha&HFF&}can I ask you to analyze these?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.97,0:13:38.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aizawa-san, can I ask you to analyze these?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.45,0:13:40.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm good at that. {\alpha&HFF&}I'll do a thorough job.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.45,0:13:42.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm good at that. I'll do a thorough job.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.36,0:13:43.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please do.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.86,0:13:48.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll confirm the contents of the copied tapes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.67,0:13:53.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How is it, Ryuuzaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.60,0:13:55.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was an interesting video.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.09,0:13:59.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If the police agree to cooperate with Kira, {\alpha&HFF&}there are orders to broadcast video three, and if they refuse, video four is to be played.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.36,0:14:02.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If the police agree to cooperate with Kira, there are orders to broadcast video three, {\alpha&HFF&}and if they refuse, video four is to be played.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.25,0:14:04.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If the police agree to cooperate with Kira, there are orders to broadcast video three, and if they refuse, video four is to be played.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.82,0:14:07.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On video three, there are detailed conditions regarding the cooperation.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.48,0:14:11.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In a nutshell, it's to report information on more criminals.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.85,0:14:14.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if they've committed less serious crimes, {\alpha&HFF&}there are instructions to pick out those who harm others, and those that abuse the weak and vulnerable.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.74,0:14:19.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if they've committed less serious crimes, there are instructions to pick out those who harm others, and those that abuse the weak and vulnerable.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.14,0:14:22.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kira will then decide whether to pass judgement on them or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.09,0:14:23.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In addition, {\alpha&HFF&}as proof that the police are willing to cooperate, they order both L and a senior member of the police to appear on TV,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.65,0:14:26.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In addition, as proof that the police are willing to cooperate, {\alpha&HFF&}they order both L and a senior member of the police to appear on TV,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.30,0:14:29.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In addition, as proof that the police are willing to cooperate, they order both L and a senior member of the police to appear on TV,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.43,0:14:33.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and announce "We will cooperate with Kira".
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.61,0:14:37.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By exposing the faces of myself and a senior policeman, {\alpha&HFF&}should the police attempt anything funny, they would be able to kill us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.53,0:14:39.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By exposing the faces of myself and a senior policeman, should the police attempt anything funny, {\alpha&HFF&}they would be able to kill us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.81,0:14:42.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By exposing the faces of myself and a senior policeman, should the police attempt anything funny, they would be able to kill us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.76,0:14:47.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about the contents of the fourth video, if we answer "no"?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.53,0:14:50.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's more or less the same thing, but said in a different way.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.24,0:14:55.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The answer is bound to be "no", Yagami-san. {\alpha&HFF&}Please authorize Sakura TV to play tape four.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.17,0:15:00.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The answer is bound to be "no", Yagami-san. Please authorize Sakura TV to play tape four.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.13,0:15:05.09,KiraVideo,,0000,0000,0000,,I think that it's a great shame that you've chosen to answer "no".
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.09,0:15:08.93,KiraVideo,,0000,0000,0000,,Since this reply indicates that the police will persistently fight against me,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.93,0:15:13.39,KiraVideo,,0000,0000,0000,,I will have to take the life of the Chief of the Japanese Police Force, or alternatively, {\alpha&HFF&}the life of the person directing this investigation, known as L.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.39,0:15:18.35,KiraVideo,,0000,0000,0000,,I will have to take the life of the Chief of the Japanese Police Force, or alternatively, the life of the person directing this investigation, known as L.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.35,0:15:20.33,KiraVideo,,0000,0000,0000,,The Chief of Police or L?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.33,0:15:25.59,KiraVideo,,0000,0000,0000,,Which one of you will pay the price for deciding not to help me create a peaceful world?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.36,0:15:28.25,KiraVideo,,0000,0000,0000,,Please decide within four days.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.11,0:15:41.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,God is on my side after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.20,0:15:42.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, when I say "God", {\alpha&HFF&}I mean "Shinigami".
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.96,0:15:45.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, when I say "God", I mean "Shinigami".
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.37,0:15:47.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.48,0:15:50.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Another Shinigami has come down to Earth, {\alpha&HFF&}and that Shinigami's Death Note has passed into the hands of a human who supports Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.98,0:15:56.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Another Shinigami has come down to Earth, and that Shinigami's Death Note has passed into the hands of a human who supports Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.70,0:16:00.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's highly probable that this Kira has the eyes of a Shinigami.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.46,0:16:02.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, {\alpha&HFF&}this Kira's ability to kill is far greater than mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.31,0:16:05.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, this Kira's ability to kill is far greater than mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.02,0:16:08.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Given the current situation, it'll be fine to leave them alone for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.15,0:16:10.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a good chance that L will be buried.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.45,0:16:13.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, {\alpha&HFF&}what I can't forgive, is that they've lowered Kira's dignity by using such inferior methods!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.01,0:16:18.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, what I can't forgive, is that they've lowered Kira's dignity by using such inferior methods!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.48,0:16:20.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll also be problematic if the fake messes up, gets caught, {\alpha&HFF&}and people find out about the Death Note.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.79,0:16:23.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll also be problematic if the fake messes up, gets caught, and people find out about the Death Note.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.91,0:16:26.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't leave them to their own devices for too long.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.15,0:16:32.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, the ideal thing for me to do would be... {\alpha&HFF&}to help out with the investigation, and grasp both L's and the fake Kira's moves.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.59,0:16:34.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, the ideal thing for me to do would be... to help out with the investigation, {\alpha&HFF&}and grasp both L's and the fake Kira's moves.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.55,0:16:38.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, the ideal thing for me to do would be... to help out with the investigation, and grasp both L's and the fake Kira's moves.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.39,0:16:43.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuzaki, {\alpha&HFF&}it's just as we thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.72,0:16:45.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuzaki, it's just as we thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.51,0:16:48.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of their own accord, world leaders have discussed this, {\alpha&HFF&}and they want the real L to appear on TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.23,0:16:51.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of their own accord, world leaders have discussed this, and they want the real L to appear on TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.22,0:16:57.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is the correct choice to make, {\alpha&HFF&}but we still have three days, so let's try and think of some countermeasures.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.51,0:16:59.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is the correct choice to make, but we still have three days, {\alpha&HFF&}so let's try and think of some countermeasures.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.89,0:17:02.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is the correct choice to make, but we still have three days, so let's try and think of some countermeasures.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.05,0:17:06.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd be pretty upset... {\alpha&HFF&}if I was killed by someone who's merely jumping onto the "Kira" bandwagon.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.10,0:17:09.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd be pretty upset... if I was killed by someone who's merely jumping onto the "Kira" bandwagon.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.04,0:17:11.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean by that, Ryuuzaki?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.39,0:17:16.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The probability of this Kira being a fake is extremely high.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.72,0:17:18.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, {\alpha&HFF&}a "second Kira" is probably a better description.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.07,0:17:20.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, a "second Kira" is probably a better description.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.22,0:17:22.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A second Kira?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.90,0:17:25.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What makes you think that there's a second Kira?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.97,0:17:27.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please explain this to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.37,0:17:29.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Firstly, {\alpha&HFF&}if you look at the first tape used to convince the TV station's employees,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.29,0:17:32.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Firstly, if you look at the first tape used to convince the TV station's employees,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.94,0:17:36.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it's noticeable that the victims of the predicted deaths, {\alpha&HFF&}were only reported on the "Wide Show" or in women's magazines.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.81,0:17:41.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it's noticeable that the victims of the predicted deaths, were only reported on the "Wide Show" or in women's magazines.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.51,0:17:46.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The real Kira wouldn't have bothered with such small fry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.76,0:17:51.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, if we think of them as a second Kira... {\alpha&HFF&}it'd have been too risky for them to use any criminal that the real Kira may potentially kill before them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.50,0:17:56.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, if we think of them as a second Kira... it'd have been too risky for them to use any criminal that the real Kira may potentially kill before them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.89,0:17:59.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuzaki, {\alpha&HFF&}what are the chances of there being a second Kira?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.43,0:18:02.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuzaki, what are the chances of there being a second Kira?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.30,0:18:05.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This time it's over 70%.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.23,0:18:09.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Either way, I don't like their methods... {\alpha&HFF&}It's unlike Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.81,0:18:11.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Either way, I don't like their methods... It's unlike Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.22,0:18:12.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Unlike"?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.81,0:18:14.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Up till now, {\alpha&HFF&}with the exception of those chasing after them, Kira has avoided sacrificing the innocent.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.06,0:18:18.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Up till now, with the exception of those chasing after them, Kira has avoided sacrificing the innocent.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.18,0:18:21.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we can catch one of the Kiras, {\alpha&HFF&}I think that we'll get hints to help catch the other.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.05,0:18:25.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we can catch one of the Kiras, I think that we'll get hints to help catch the other.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.49,0:18:28.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yagami-san, {\alpha&HFF&}would it be okay if we asked your son to help us in the investigation?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.23,0:18:32.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yagami-san, would it be okay if we asked your son to help us in the investigation?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.26,0:18:34.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, {\alpha&HFF&}am I to understand that you no longer suspect him?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.13,0:18:37.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, am I to understand that you no longer suspect him?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.86,0:18:39.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, {\alpha&HFF&}I can't say that I don't still suspect him, but I am counting on his skills of deduction.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.04,0:18:41.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I can't say that I don't still suspect him, {\alpha&HFF&}but I am counting on his skills of deduction.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.33,0:18:43.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I can't say that I don't still suspect him, but I am counting on his skills of deduction.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.28,0:18:45.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's what you mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.82,0:18:50.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If this is what my son wants, I see no reason to stop him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.81,0:18:52.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.23,0:18:53.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, {\alpha&HFF&}please don't tell him that we suspect that this Kira may be a fake.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.85,0:18:59.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, please don't tell him that we suspect that this Kira may be a fake.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.66,0:19:03.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please give the impression that we're determinedly pursuing one Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.87,0:19:11.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Misa... {\alpha&HFF&}I kindly gave that Death Note to you, so why don't you use it more for yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.60,0:19:14.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Misa... I kindly gave that Death Note to you, {\alpha&HFF&}so why don't you use it more for yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.29,0:19:18.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Misa... I kindly gave that Death Note to you, so why don't you use it more for yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.26,0:19:20.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am using it for myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.28,0:19:22.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, I support Kira!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.79,0:19:24.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I want to know what kind of person Kira is.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.60,0:19:28.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I want to meet and talk to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.60,0:19:34.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I went through the trouble of sending those tapes to the TV station, and ensured that I could get Kira to notice me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.31,0:19:37.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kira will be interested. {\alpha&HFF&}I'm sure of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.68,0:19:38.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kira will be interested. I'm sure of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.07,0:19:40.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a dangerous game you're playing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.27,0:19:43.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You could be killed. {\alpha&HFF&}You know that, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.44,0:19:44.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You could be killed. You know that, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.35,0:19:47.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be okay. {\alpha&HFF&}I'm sure Kira is kind to innocent girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.00,0:19:50.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be okay. I'm sure Kira is kind to innocent girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.00,0:19:51.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And if it does come to that...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.62,0:19:54.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Misa is stronger because she has the eyes!
